</big><br><small>"Tails are not for biting or pulling!"</small></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uslagfestbloodsoul.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Slagfest Bloodsoul</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 32<br> <font color=#FF0000>(9/10/02 2:16:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3858.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Equiping a MT...</span><hr size=1> Honestly i find a prob w/ giving all the best equip to 1 toon..let alone a recent addition to the guild.<br>
<br>
